                                <a class="post__cat cat-54 " href="https://grizzlyreports.com/category/news/"> news&nbsp;</a><a class="post__cat cat-114 " href="https://grizzlyreports.com/category/ottobock/">Ottobock SE &amp; Co. KGaA</a>                                </div>
								<h1 class="post-title typescale-4">Grizzly CEO Eggert Interviewed by CNBC Regarding Ottobock</h1>
																<!-- Entry meta -->
<div class="entry-meta">
	<span class="entry-author entry-author--with-ava">
        By <a class="entry-author__name" title="Posts by Grizzly Research" rel="author" href="https://grizzlyreports.com/author/grizzly-research/">Grizzly Research</a>  </span>
    
    <time class="time published"
          datetime="2026-05-20T13:33:54-04:00"
          title="May 20, 2026 1:33 pm">
        <i class="mdicon mdicon-schedule"></i>May 20, 2026    </time>
</div>							</header>
                            
                            <div class="single-body entry-content typography-copy">
                                                                <p>Our CEO, Siegfried Eggert, appeared in CNBC Squawk Box Europe for an interview regarding Grizzly&#8217;s criticism on Ottobock SE &amp; Co. KGaA on May 19.</p>
<div align="center">
<iframe src="https://player.cnbc.com/p/gZWlPC/cnbc_global?playertype=synd&amp;byGuid=7000413354" width="560" height="349" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>
</div>
<p><i style="font-size:10pt;">Images by CNBC Squawk Box Europe.</i></p>
							</div>
                                                                                    <div class="post__footer">
    <div class="row row--flex row--vertical-center">
		<div class="col-xs-5">
			<div class="social-share text-left"><ul class="social-list social-list--md list-horizontal"><li><a onClick="window.open('http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgrizzlyreports.com%2Fgrizzly-ceo-eggert-interviewed-by-cnbc-regarding-ottobock%2F','Facebook','width=600,height=300,left='+(screen.availWidth/2-300)+',top='+(screen.availHeight/2-150)+''); return false;" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgrizzlyreports.com%2Fgrizzly-ceo-eggert-interviewed-by-cnbc-regarding-ottobock%2F"><div class="share-item__icon"><i class="mdicon mdicon-facebook " title="Facebook"></i></div></a></li><li><a onClick="window.open('http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgrizzlyreports.com%2Fgrizzly-ceo-eggert-interviewed-by-cnbc-regarding-ottobock%2F&amp;text=Grizzly%20CEO%20Eggert%20Interviewed%20by%20CNBC%20Regarding%20Ottobock','Twitter share','width=600,height=300,left='+(screen.availWidth/2-300)+',top='+(screen.availHeight/2-150)+''); return false;" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fgrizzlyreports.com%2Fgrizzly-ceo-eggert-interviewed-by-cnbc-regarding-ottobock%2F&amp;text=Grizzly%20CEO%20Eggert%20Interviewed%20by%20CNBC%20Regarding%20Ottobock"><div class="share-item__icon"><i class="mdicon mdicon-twitter " title="Twitter"></i></div></a></li><li><a onClick="window.open('http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fgrizzlyreports.com%2Fgrizzly-ceo-eggert-interviewed-by-cnbc-regarding-ottobock%2F','Linkedin','width=863,height=500,left='+(screen.availWidth/2-431)+',top='+(screen.availHeight/2-250)+''); return false;" href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fgrizzlyreports.com%2Fgrizzly-ceo-eggert-interviewed-by-cnbc-regarding-ottobock%2F"><div class="share-item__icon"><i class="mdicon mdicon-linkedin " title="Linkedin"></i></div></a></li></ul></div>        </div>
